| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0876 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d0dda17c-4452-54c4-94cd-7cc9c4c962f7"
